# Copy this file to .env (or .env.local) and fill in the values.
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the browser.

# ── Maps — Amazon Location Service v2 GeoMaps (optional) ───────────────────
# Renders every map in the app (the vehicle location map and the Check route
# planner) using the v2 GeoMaps Standard style in Truck travel mode — i.e. with
# truck-restriction overlays (height/weight/bridge/tunnel and hazmat shields)
# baked into the basemap. The in-app toggle only switches the light/dark theme.
#
# Only the key + region are required; if either is missing the map UI shows a
# themed "not configured" state and the rest of the app is unaffected.
#
#   VITE_AWS_LOCATION_API_KEY   the Amazon Location API key VALUE (looks like
#                               "v1.public.xxxxx") — NOT the key ARN. This is a
#                               READ-ONLY key; its policy must allow GetTile on
#                               the v2 style plus geo-places:Geocode and
#                               geo-places:SearchText (company/POI + address
#                               search in the planner) and
#                               geo-routes:CalculateRoutes for the route planner.
#                               geo-routes:SnapToRoads is also recommended so a
#                               dragged route/waypoint snaps to the nearest road
#                               (it falls back to the raw drop point without it).
#                               Tracker reads happen on the server with separate
#                               IAM credentials.
#   VITE_AWS_LOCATION_REGION    the key's region, e.g. eu-central-1
#
# The Check route planner can also switch the basemap to Satellite / Hybrid
# (satellite + labels) and overlay Amazon Location's own real-time traffic
# (congestion / construction / incidents, via the `traffic=All` style parameter).
# All of these use the same key — no extra config or provider needed.
#
# Style URL used:
#   https://maps.geo.${region}.amazonaws.com/v2/styles/Standard/descriptor?travel-modes=Truck&color-scheme=Dark&key=…
VITE_AWS_LOCATION_API_KEY=
VITE_AWS_LOCATION_REGION=eu-central-1
